---
title: Chermoula Pork Burger with Caramelised Onion, Slaw & Rainbow Veggie Fries
description: Mix up a pork patty infused with the crowd favourite chermoula spice blend! With tender, caramelised onion to add a touch of
sweetness, plus a hearty side of veggie fries, this meal packs flavour in every bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-pork-burger-84188dc2.jpg
